(BUZZING)

206
00:12:14,625 --> 00:12:16,961
FEMALE AUTOMATED VOICE:
<i>Pressure stable.</i>

207
00:12:49,393 --> 00:12:50,629
(BREATHING RAPIDLY)

208
00:12:52,596 --> 00:12:54,031
(SCREAMING IN PAIN)

209
