215
00:15:04,695 --> 00:15:08,099
(EXHALING DEEPLY)

216
00:15:16,374 --> 00:15:18,109
Fuck.

217
00:15:47,305 --> 00:15:48,604
Okay.

218
00:15:48,605 --> 00:15:50,140
<i>Okay.</i>

219
00:15:52,009 --> 00:15:56,180
<i>Hello, this is Mark
Watney, astronaut.</i>

220
00:15:56,815 --> 00:15:59,949
<i>I'm entering this
log for the record...</i>

221
00:15:59,950 --> 00:16:02,553
<i>in case I don't make it.</i>

222
00:16:04,955 --> 00:16:09,258
<i>It is 06:53 on Sol 19...</i>

223
00:16:09,259 --> 00:16:12,329
<i>and I'm alive.</i>

224
00:16:13,398 --> 00:16:14,964
<i>Obviously.</i>

225
00:16:14,965 --> 00:16:17,501
<i>But I'm guessing that's
gonna come as a surprise</i>

226
00:16:17,502 --> 00:16:20,970
<i>to my crewmates and to NASA.</i>

227
00:16:20,971 --> 00:16:23,707
<i>And to the entire
world, really, so...</i>

228
00:16:26,476 --> 00:16:28,312
<i>Surprise.</i>

229
00:16:29,479 --> 00:16:31,849
<i>I did not die on Sol 18.</i>

230
00:16:31,850 --> 00:16:33,983
<i>Best I can figure...</i>

231
00:16:33,984 --> 00:16:36,219
<i>this length of our primary
communications antenna</i>

232
00:16:36,220 --> 00:16:37,686
<i>broke off...</i>

233
00:16:37,687 --> 00:16:39,922
<i>and tore through my bio-monitor...</i>

234
00:16:39,923 --> 00:16:42,459
<i>and ripped a hole in me as well.</i>

235
00:16:43,194 --> 00:16:46,296
<i>But the antenna and
the blood, really,</i>

236
00:16:46,297 --> 00:16:48,498
<i>managed to seal the
breach in my suit...</i>

237
00:16:48,499 --> 00:16:50,200
<i>which kept me alive,</i>

238
00:16:50,201 --> 00:16:52,603
<i>even though the crew must
have thought I was dead.</i>

239
00:16:53,370 --> 00:16:56,073
<i>I have no way to contact NASA.</i>

240
00:16:56,074 --> 00:16:59,041
<i>And even if I could, it's
gonna be four years...</i>

241
00:16:59,042 --> 00:17:01,478
<i>until a manned mission can reach me.</i>

242
00:17:02,345 --> 00:17:04,915
<i>And I'm in a Hab
designed to last 31 days.</i>

243
00:17:04,916 --> 00:17:07,317
<i>If the oxygenator breaks,
I'm gonna suffocate.</i>

244
00:17:07,318 --> 00:17:09,953
