1023
01:13:54,688 --> 01:13:56,489
Is the probe going to be ready on time?

1024
01:13:56,490 --> 01:13:58,425
- BRUCE: <i>We're behind.</i>
- Give me a number.

1025
01:13:58,426 --> 01:14:01,928
<i>15 days. 15 days and
I can get it done.</i>

1026
01:14:01,929 --> 01:14:03,128
