1043
01:14:38,031 --> 01:14:39,498
Teddy.

1044
01:14:39,499 --> 01:14:41,368
- Sir, if that ever got out...
- It's on me.

1045
01:14:41,369 --> 01:14:42,769
You got your two weeks.

1046
01:14:42,770 --> 01:14:44,172
Get it done.

1047
01:14:45,138 --> 01:14:47,406
