1077
01:16:34,781 --> 01:16:35,849
TIMER CONTROLLER: <i>Proceeding
with the count.</i>

1078
01:16:35,850 --> 01:16:37,316
<i>10... 9...</i>

1079
01:16:37,317 --> 01:16:38,819
<i>8...</i>

1080
01:16:38,820 --> 01:16:40,186
<i>7... 6...</i>

1081
01:16:40,187 --> 01:16:41,855
