L.O.S. here, too.

1109
01:18:14,013 --> 01:18:15,381
CAPCOM TECHNICIAN: <i>U.S.
Destroyer</i> Stockton

1110
01:18:15,382 --> 01:18:17,550
<i>reporting debris
falling from the sky.</i>

1111
01:18:17,551 --> 01:18:18,685
TIMER CONTROLLER:
<i>Everyone in the LCC,</i>

1112
01:18:18,686 --> 01:18:20,153
<i>maintain your positions
at your consoles.</i>

1113
01:18:20,154 --> 01:18:22,422
GC, lock the doors.

1114
01:18:50,785 --> 01:18:52,851
WATNEY: <i>"Commander Lewis...</i>

1115
01:18:52,852 --> 01:18:56,523
<i>"I may need you to
do something for me.</i>

1116
01:18:58,092 --> 01:19:03,064
<i>"If I die, I need you to
check in on my parents.</i>

1117
01:19:04,164 --> 01:19:07,534
<i>"They'll wanna hear all
about our time here on Mars.</i>

1118
01:19:09,035 --> 01:19:11,171
<i>"I know that sucks.</i>

1119
01:19:11,172 --> 01:19:14,475
<i>"And it'll be hard
talking to a couple...</i>

1120
01:19:15,275 --> 01:19:17,912
<i>"about their dead son.</i>

1121
01:19:18,544 --> 01:19:20,547
"It's a lot to ask.

1122
01:19:22,782 --> 01:19:25,219
"Which is why I'm asking you.

1123
01:19:26,152 --> 01:19:28,387
<i>"I'm not giving up.</i>

1124
01:19:28,388 --> 01:19:33,360
<i>"We just need to prepare
for every outcome.</i>

1125
01:19:34,762 --> 01:19:37,064
"Please tell them...

1126
01:19:38,798 --> 01:19:40,967
"Tell them I love what I do...

1127
01:19:45,173 --> 01:19:46,574
"and I'm really good at it.

1128
01:19:49,176 --> 01:19:52,346
<i>"And that I'm dying...</i>

1129
01:19:53,446 --> 01:19:56,182
"for something big...

1130
01:19:57,451 --> 01:19:59,653
"and beautiful...

1131
01:20:03,490 --> 01:20:05,660
"and greater than me.

1132
01:20:07,594 --> 01:20:10,230
<i>"Tell them I said I
can live with that.</i>

1133
01:20:11,130 --> 01:20:13,000
<i>"And tell them...</i>

1134
01:20:14,000 --> 01:20:17,637
<i>"thank you for being
my mom and dad."</i>

1135
01:20:20,039 --> 01:20:21,708
VINCENT: <i>We substituted
protein cubes</i>

1136
01:20:21,709 --> 01:20:23,577
<i>for the standard rations.</i>

1137
01:20:23,578 --> 01:20:25,544
<i>The thrust of the launch combined</i>

1138
01:20:25,545 --> 01:20:27,379
<i>with the simultaneous
lateral vibration...</i>

1139
01:20:27,380 --> 01:20:32,150
<i>liquefied the cubes and
created an unbalanced load.</i>

1140
01:20:32,151 --> 01:20:33,552
<i>Vincent, why wasn't this addressed</i>

1141
01:20:33,553 --> 01:20:35,422
<i>in the inspections phase?</i>

1142
01:20:35,423 --> 01:20:37,022
<i>In order to make our launch window,</i>

1143
01:20:37,023 --> 01:20:39,559
<i>we were forced to
accelerate our schedule.</i>

1144
01:20:39,560 --> 01:20:40,728
(BOTH SPEAKING MANDARIN)

1145
01:21:31,277 --> 01:21:32,479
SANDERS: Yes.

