1151
01:21:47,061 --> 01:21:48,793
Thanks to my uncle Tommy in China,

1152
01:21:48,794 --> 01:21:50,930
we get another chance at this.

1153
01:21:50,931 --> 01:21:54,233
Now, we finished the
<i>Iris</i> probe in 62 days.

